query:
INSERT INTO requirements (frameworkId, articleNumber, title, description, category, riskLevelApplicable, isMandatory) VALUES 
-- EU AI Act Risk Management
(1, 'Art. 9', 'Risk Management System', 'Establish, implement, document and maintain a risk management system for high-risk AI systems.', 'Risk Management', 'high', 1),
(1, 'Art. 9.2', 'Risk Identification', 'Identify and analyze known and foreseeable risks associated with each high-risk AI system.', 'Risk Management', 'high', 1),
(1, 'Art. 9.4', 'Risk Mitigation', 'Adopt suitable risk management measures to eliminate or reduce risks as far as possible.', 'Risk Management', 'high', 1),
-- EU AI Act Data Governance
(1, 'Art. 10', 'Data Governance', 'Training, validation and testing data sets shall be subject to appropriate data governance practices.', 'Data Governance', 'high', 1),
(1, 'Art. 10.2', 'Data Quality', 'Ensure training data is relevant, representative, free of errors and complete.', 'Data Governance', 'high', 1),
(1, 'Art. 10.3', 'Bias Examination', 'Examine training data for possible biases that could affect health, safety, or fundamental rights.', 'Data Governance', 'high', 1),
-- EU AI Act Technical Documentation
(1, 'Art. 11', 'Technical Documentation', 'Draw up technical documentation before placing high-risk AI system on market.', 'Documentation', 'high', 1),
(1, 'Art. 11.1', 'Documentation Content', 'Include general description, design specifications, monitoring, and validation information.', 'Documentation', 'high', 1),
-- EU AI Act Transparency
(1, 'Art. 13', 'Transparency Requirements', 'High-risk AI systems shall be designed to enable users to interpret system output appropriately.', 'Transparency', 'high', 1),
(1, 'Art. 13.3', 'Instructions for Use', 'Provide clear instructions including intended purpose, level of accuracy, and known limitations.', 'Transparency', 'high', 1),
-- EU AI Act Human Oversight
(1, 'Art. 14', 'Human Oversight', 'High-risk AI systems shall be designed to be effectively overseen by natural persons.', 'Human Oversight', 'high', 1),
(1, 'Art. 14.4', 'Override Capability', 'Ensure human operators can intervene, interrupt, or override the AI system.', 'Human Oversight', 'high', 1);
